1.1.name: wordpress/discover
1.1.description: A very neat and clean orange and white business theme. The theme is fully responsive that looks great on any device. The theme supports widgets. And features theme-options, threaded-comments and multi-level dropdown menu. A simple and neat typography. Uses WordPress custom menu, header image, and background. discover is WooCommerce Compatible. Get free support on http://antthemes.com/forum
